---
title: "Drive Software: Aurelia Widgets"
excerpt: "A good start for widgets in bootstrap"
tags: [aurelia]
---

It's definitely not the only one around but it's always good to see another [widgets library](https://github.com/drivesoftware/aurelia-widgets) for aurelia. I think if you're starting your own project it's a good idea to create your own just to understand how things work under the covers.